Aims:
- Discuss individual roles
- Discuss high level roles

Minutes:
- 2-wheel drive differential
- Design philosophy: correctness, simple, speed (in order)
- Ability to rotate on the spot
- We want to see forward, left, right
- Poles serve as a measuring unit (change in distance from plywood to pole)
- Sensors in the centre for point of reference/centering
- Need status led
- 2 lidars on left/right side to make sure perpendicular to wall via triangulation
- 1 lidar on left and 1 lidar on right to detect drift from centre (make sure perpendicular). Won't work with gap in wall.
